HOUSE BILL 157
By Eldridge
SENATE BILL 978
By Southerland
AN ACT to amend Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 4-
3-1205; Title 39, Chapter 17, Part 18; Title 52,
Chapter 8; Section 68-1-904; Title 68, Chapter 11,
Part 2 and Title 71, relative to services for adults.
BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 4-3-1205, is amended by deleting
"adult day care" wherever it appears in subdivision (5) and substituting instead "adult day
services".
SECTION 2. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 39-17-1802, is amended by deleting
"adult day care" in subdivision (9) and substituting instead "adult day services".
SECTION 3. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 39-17-1803, is amended by deleting
"adult day care" in subdivision (a)(3) and substituting instead "adult day services".
SECTION 4. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 52-8-203, is amended by deleting
"adult day care" wherever it appears in subdivision (a)(5) and substituting instead "adult day
services".
SECTION 5. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 71-1-105, is amended by deleting
"adult day care" in subdivision (a)(5)(A) and substituting instead "adult day services" and
deleting "adult day care services" in subdivision (a)(5)(C) and substituting instead "adult day
services".
SECTION 6. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 71-2-401, is amended by deleting
"Adult day care" wherever it appears and substituting instead "Adult day services" and by
deleting "adult day care services" wherever it appears and substituting instead "adult day
services".
